      <title>耶伦与中国同意举行旨在“平衡增长”的会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/yellen-china-s-he-commit-to-talks-focused-on-balanced-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦和中国国务院副总理何立峰同意启动正式会谈，旨在解决美国和其他国家认为的中国日​​益严重的工业产能过剩问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/yellen-china-s-he-commit-to-talks-focused-on-balanced-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 06:25:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>如果苏纳克在地方选举后无法坚持下去，保守党将考虑由莫当特领导的联合内阁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/uk-conservatives-weigh-unity-cabinet-under-mordaunt-if-rishi-sunak-can-t-hang-on</link>
      <description><![CDATA[下个月的英国地方选举对里希·苏纳克来说是最危险的时刻。越来越多的保守党议员正在密切关注保守党的表现，考虑 B 计划可能是什么样子。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/uk-conservatives-weigh-unity-cabinet-under-mordaunt-if-rishi-sunak-can-t-hang-on</guid>
